</m:mrow>
<m:mrow>
<m:mn> 9 </m:mn>
</m:mrow>
</m:mfrac>
</m:mtd>
</m:mtr>
</m:mtable>
</m:math>
</para>
<para id="element-44">
Similarly, the MI of the right rod is :
</para>
<para id="element-45">
<m:math display="block">
<m:mtable columnalign="left">
<m:mtr>
<m:mtd>
<m:msub>
<m:mi> I </m:mi>
<m:mi> OR </m:mi>
</m:msub>
<m:mo> = </m:mo> 
